{"id":1355,"date":"2018-08-06T13:22:27","date_gmt":"2018-08-06T17:22:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=professeur&#038;p=1355"},"modified":"2023-06-12T12:04:40","modified_gmt":"2023-06-12T16:04:40","slug":"pascal-belleau","status":"publish","type":"professeur","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/equipe\/pascal-belleau\/","title":{"rendered":"Pascal Belleau"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Pascal Belleau a \u00e9tudi\u00e9 au Conservatoire d\u2019art dramatique et fait une ma\u00eetrise \u00e0 l\u2019UQ\u00c0M. Il a jou\u00e9 au th\u00e9\u00e2tre et \u00e0 la t\u00e9l\u00e9vision et a fait de nombreuses mises en sc\u00e8ne dont sept \u00e0 son th\u00e9\u00e2tre, Le th\u00e9\u00e2tre Masson. Il enseigne avec passion l\u2019interpr\u00e9tation depuis 1985 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9cole Sup\u00e9rieure de Th\u00e9\u00e2tre de l\u2019UQAM, depuis 1992 au c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>\u00ab\u00a0La cr\u00e9ation ne s\u2019inspire pas de ce qui est, mais de ce qui pourrait \u00eatre, non du r\u00e9el, mais du possible\u00a0\u00bb Rudolf Steiner<\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2250,"template":"","categorie-equipe":[202],"departement-equipe":[295],"specialite-equipe":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-1355","professeur","type-professeur","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorie-equipe-personnel-enseignant","departement-equipe-theatre"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur\/1355","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/professeur"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/professeur"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2250"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/